scenes.description: MC section with Calliope Mori and Takanashi Kiara on the red carpet, interacting with the audience and hyping up the show.
Ninomae Ina'nis performs the song 'Future Island' (未来来島) on a circular stage surrounded by digital cityscapes.
Gawr Gura performs her song 'CHIMERA' on stage with a visual transition and energetic choreography.
